{"tid":24681,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（賭學）賭邊瓣自己最有把握呀","createTime":"2016-12-05T16:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T02:45:32.000Z","uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa95e92bb5a7e20eed4216c9d0a11ef31f0edcc","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"我會玩波，馬，21點，百家樂，大細，花旗骰<br />\n<br />\n始終玩來玩去，研究極暫時都係得賭波有正數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家交流下心得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818179186fb290ec00698289c789f4f0bfd22f7d","tid":24681,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"十五糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854c45ab999f48cc5950d298ea38bb1893934b63","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94010178cc8f2404e3643096ee41759695334f11","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"冇人賭嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfc0ac36a1102a13e62d38fbac3395e524b5958","tid":24681,"uid":25080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"波有冇心得先"},{"pid":"8345333e5377a69ee11678ba89d6653b9ed5f5a9","tid":24681,"uid":4219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"賭自己輸我最有把握 從來都冇運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連40蚊六合彩都冇中過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70759784acca32c46121bd2b71fdd43ec6df07f","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波有冇心得先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常買開讓球盤，我ge心得係會揀一場其中一隊大量傷兵，買佢輸，好似尋晚比勒費爾德對波琴，波琴傷撚曬d人，比勒讓平半贏到1:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋大細我偏向買細，因大家對攻，黑起上離兩隊20次射門都可以唔入<br />\n角球大細我偏向買大，有機會角球駁角球<br />\n大約係咁先，大家再討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac72632d9cccc4c63c8c4d78d7e5baef16ce4c7d","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賭自己輸我最有把握 從來都冇運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連40蚊六合彩都冇中過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你唔係期期買呀？<br />\n我六合彩又係冇咩運，對上果次見唔知咩金多寶，人生第一次買7個字，上網睇埋果d咩最常出現號碼離買，都可以一個字都唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我現在only賭波，唔會賭好大，贏下日常生活洗費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上個月好運，開到條路8連勝！賭波贏夠每日d飯錢玩錢，成個月係提款機only按左一次錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今個月冇咩運lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bc77dfeb1b5da2b6779e8dc8e5a47d02532384","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3aefb836c527acd5f390beb1a4ac733bf4a9be","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d06607113d02f0279c850f41e2b4be1c39cc004","tid":24681,"uid":56544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T22:44:41.000Z","msg":"不賭就是贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab5f31422b0e2758f894196935051027a45d008","tid":24681,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}